"title": "4027: world, as fallen",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4027",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The world has fallen into sin and rebellion against its Creator. As a result, it has come under the power of Satan.</p>\n<h2>The world is under the power of Satan</h2>\n<h3>He is prince of this world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:30\">JHN 14:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:4\">1JN 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>He holds the world in his grasp</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:19\">1JN 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:4\">EPH 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h2>The world is opposed to God</h2>\n<h3>It is evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:7\">JHN 7:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:19-John3:20\">JHN 3:19–3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:4\">GAL 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15-1John2:16\">1JN 2:15–2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Evil extends to the unseen world of the heavenly realms</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12\">EPH 6:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>It is opposed to God's wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:6-1Cor2:8\">1CO 2:6–2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:19\">1CO 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>It is opposed to the life of faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:18-John15:19\">JHN 15:18–15:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:10-John1:11\">JHN 1:10–1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:6\">JHN 17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:9\">JHN 17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14-John17:18\">JHN 17:14–17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:25\">JHN 17:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:4\">JAS 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>It is opposed to Jesus Christ's kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:36\">JHN 18:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:23\">ISA 40:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:8-Matt4:10\">MAT 4:8–4:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:5-Luke4:8\">LUK 4:5–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:14\">MAT 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:30\">LUK 12:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:23\">JHN 8:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:17\">JHN 14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:3\">2CO 10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:38\">HEB 11:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:11</a></p>\n<h2>The world is under judgment</h2>\n<h3>It is condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:32\">1CO 11:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5-Gen6:7\">GEN 6:5–6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:4\">GEN 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:21\">GEN 7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">ISA 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:8\">ZEP 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:7\">MAT 18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:11\">JHN 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:17\">1JN 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>It will be judged in righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:8\">PSA 9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:13\">PSA 96:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:9\">ISA 26:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:5-Nah1:6\">NAM 1:5–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:19\">ROM 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>It will be judged by the saints</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:2\">1CO 6:2</a></p>",
